{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":837,"text":"How much do you need\nto know about a person"},{"time":2862,"text":"before you'd feel comfortable\nmaking a loan?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":6044,"text":"Suppose you wanted to lend 1,000 dollars"},{"time":8523,"text":"to the person sitting two rows behind you."},{"time":11190,"text":"What would you need to know\nabout that person"},{"time":13346,"text":"before you'd feel comfortable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15291,"text":"My mom came to the US from India\nin her late thirties."},{"time":19614,"text":"She's a doctor in Brooklyn,"},{"time":21070,"text":"and she often lets friends and neighbors\ncome to see her for health services,"},{"time":25317,"text":"whether they can pay right away or not."},{"time":27955,"text":"I remember running into her patients\nwith her at the grocery store"},{"time":31186,"text":"or on the sidewalk,"},{"time":32361,"text":"and sometimes they would come\nand pay her right on the spot"},{"time":35225,"text":"for previous appointments."},{"time":36607,"text":"She would thank them,"},{"time":37870,"text":"and ask them about their families\nand their health."},{"time":41466,"text":"She gave them credit\nbecause she trusted them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45122,"text":"Most of us are like my mom."},{"time":47899,"text":"We would give credit to someone we know"},{"time":50786,"text":"or that we live next to."},{"time":52206,"text":"But most of us are probably not\ngoing to lend to a stranger"},{"time":55934,"text":"unless we know a little\nsomething about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59634,"text":"Banks, credit card companies\nand other financial institutions"},{"time":63361,"text":"don't know us on a personal level,"},{"time":65645,"text":"but they do have a way of trusting us,"},{"time":68548,"text":"and that's through our credit scores."},{"time":71033,"text":"Our credit scores have been created"},{"time":73052,"text":"through an aggregation and analysis\nof our public consumer credit data."},{"time":77596,"text":"And because of them, we have\npretty much easy access"},{"time":80861,"text":"to all of the goods\nand services that we need,"},{"time":83329,"text":"from getting electricity to buying a home,"},{"time":86197,"text":"or taking a risk and starting a business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89561,"text":"But ..."},{"time":90746,"text":"there are 2.5 billion people\naround the world"},{"time":95137,"text":"that don't have a credit score."},{"time":97247,"text":"That's a third of the world's population."},{"time":100930,"text":"They don't have a score"},{"time":102209,"text":"because there are no formal\npublic records on them --"},{"time":105494,"text":"no bank accounts,"},{"time":106882,"text":"no credit histories"},{"time":108400,"text":"and no social security numbers."},{"time":110482,"text":"And because they don't have a score,"},{"time":112225,"text":"they don't have access\nto the credit or financial products"},{"time":116900,"text":"that can improve their lives."},{"time":119509,"text":"They are not trusted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122968,"text":"So we wanted to find a way to build trust"},{"time":126162,"text":"and to open up financial access\nfor these 2.5 billion."},{"time":130772,"text":"So we created a mobile application"},{"time":133262,"text":"that builds credit scores for them\nusing mobile data."},{"time":138345,"text":"There are currently over one billion\nsmartphones in emerging markets."},{"time":142825,"text":"And people are using them\nthe same way that we do."},{"time":146235,"text":"They're texting their friends,\nthey're looking up directions,"},{"time":149228,"text":"they're browsing the Internet"},{"time":150664,"text":"and they're even making\nfinancial transactions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153167,"text":"Over time, this data is getting\ncaptured on our phones,"},{"time":156377,"text":"and it provides a really rich picture\nof a person's life."},{"time":161132,"text":"Our customers give us access to this data"},{"time":163332,"text":"and we capture it\nthrough our mobile application."},{"time":166466,"text":"It helps us understand\nthe creditworthiness"},{"time":169134,"text":"of people like Jenipher,\na small-business owner in Nairobi, Kenya."},{"time":174290,"text":"Jenipher is 65 years old, and for decades\nhas been running a food stall"},{"time":179197,"text":"in the central business district."},{"time":181897,"text":"She has three sons who she put\nthrough vocational school,"},{"time":185120,"text":"and she's also the leader\nof her local chama,"},{"time":187668,"text":"or savings group."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189609,"text":"Jenipher's food stall does well."},{"time":191556,"text":"She makes just enough every day\nto cover her expenses."},{"time":195024,"text":"But she's not financially secure."},{"time":197842,"text":"Any emergency could force her into debt."},{"time":200887,"text":"And she has no discretionary income"},{"time":202758,"text":"to improve her family's way of living,"},{"time":205020,"text":"for emergencies,"},{"time":206283,"text":"or for investing\ninto growing her business."},{"time":210065,"text":"If Jenipher wants credit,\nher options are limited."},{"time":213733,"text":"She could get a microloan,"},{"time":215135,"text":"but she'd have to form a group\nthat could help vouch for her credibility."},{"time":219003,"text":"And even then, the loan sizes\nwould be way too small"},{"time":221999,"text":"to really have an impact on her business,"},{"time":224280,"text":"averaging around 150 dollars."},{"time":227525,"text":"Loan sharks are always an option,"},{"time":230067,"text":"but with interest rates\nthat are well above 300 percent,"},{"time":234041,"text":"they're financially risky."},{"time":236079,"text":"And because Jenipher doesn't have\ncollateral or a credit history,"},{"time":240088,"text":"she can't walk into a bank\nand ask for a business loan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244331,"text":"But one day,"},{"time":245678,"text":"Jenipher's son convinced her\nto download our application"},{"time":249680,"text":"and apply for a loan."},{"time":251407,"text":"Jenipher answered a few\nquestions on her phone"},{"time":253970,"text":"and she gave us access to a few\nkey data points on her device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258561,"text":"And here's what we saw."},{"time":260392,"text":"So, bad news first."},{"time":262996,"text":"Jenipher had a low savings balance\nand no previous loan history."},{"time":268395,"text":"These are factors"},{"time":269570,"text":"that would have thrown up\na red flag to a traditional bank."},{"time":272620,"text":"But there were other points\nin her history that showed us"},{"time":275375,"text":"a much richer picture of her potential."},{"time":279342,"text":"So for one,"},{"time":280517,"text":"we saw that she made regular\nphone calls to her family in Uganda."},{"time":285629,"text":"Well, it turns out that the data shows"},{"time":288110,"text":"a four percent increase in repayment"},{"time":290868,"text":"among people who consistently\ncommunicate with a few close contacts."},{"time":296657,"text":"We could also see"},{"time":297840,"text":"that though she traveled\naround a lot throughout the day,"},{"time":300672,"text":"she actually had pretty\nregular travel patterns,"},{"time":303427,"text":"and she was either at home\nor at her food stall."},{"time":307315,"text":"And the data shows\na six percent increase in repayment"},{"time":311326,"text":"among customers who are consistent"},{"time":313737,"text":"with where they spend most of their time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317349,"text":"We could also see\nthat she communicated a lot"},{"time":319954,"text":"with many different people\nthroughout the day"},{"time":322326,"text":"and that she had a strong support network."},{"time":325287,"text":"Our data shows"},{"time":326704,"text":"that people who communicate\nwith more than 58 different contacts"},{"time":331408,"text":"tend to be more likely\nto be good borrowers."},{"time":334333,"text":"In Jenipher's case,"},{"time":335626,"text":"she communicated\nwith 89 different individuals,"},{"time":339693,"text":"which showed a nine percent\nincrease in her repayment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343888,"text":"These are just some of the thousands\nof different data points"},{"time":347679,"text":"that we look at to understand\na person's creditworthiness."},{"time":351397,"text":"And after analyzing all\nof these different data points,"},{"time":354494,"text":"we took the first risk"},{"time":356490,"text":"and gave Jenipher a loan."},{"time":359370,"text":"This is data that would not\nbe found on a paper trail"},{"time":362720,"text":"or in any formal financial record."},{"time":365720,"text":"But it proves trust."},{"time":368193,"text":"By looking beyond income,"},{"time":370194,"text":"we can see that people in emerging markets"},{"time":372375,"text":"that may seem risky\nand unpredictable on the surface"},{"time":376068,"text":"are actually willing and have\nthe capacity to repay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381334,"text":"Our credit scores have helped us deliver\nover 200,000 loans in Kenya"},{"time":386543,"text":"in just the past year."},{"time":388164,"text":"And our repayment rates\nare above 90 percent --"},{"time":391490,"text":"which, by the way, is in line\nwith traditional bank repayment rates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397564,"text":"With something as simple\nas a credit score,"},{"time":400497,"text":"we're giving people the power\nto build their own futures."},{"time":404647,"text":"Our customers have used\ntheir loans for family expenses,"},{"time":407978,"text":"emergencies, travel"},{"time":409859,"text":"and for investing back\ninto growing their businesses."},{"time":413792,"text":"They're now building better\neconomies and communities"},{"time":417288,"text":"where more people can succeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420664,"text":"Over the past two years\nof using our product,"},{"time":423416,"text":"Jenipher has increased\nher savings by 60 percent."},{"time":427624,"text":"She's also started\ntwo additional food stalls"},{"time":430300,"text":"and is now making plans\nfor her own restaurant."},{"time":433401,"text":"She's applying for a small-business loan\nfrom a commercial bank,"},{"time":436829,"text":"because she now has the credit history\nto prove she deserves it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442038,"text":"I saw Jenipher in Nairobi just last week,"},{"time":444977,"text":"and she told me how excited\nshe was to get started."},{"time":448252,"text":"She said,"},{"time":450178,"text":"\"Only my son believed I could do this.\nI didn't think this was for me.\""},{"time":456250,"text":"She's lived her whole life"},{"time":458560,"text":"believing that there was a part\nof the world that was closed off to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463536,"text":"Our job now is to open\nthe world to Jenipher"},{"time":467916,"text":"and the billions like her\nthat deserve to be trusted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472135,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473318,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}